    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>This plugin adds a <a href=\"https://indieweb.org/Microsub\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Microsub</a> endpoint to your WordPress site by using the hosted <a href=\"https://aperture.p3k.io\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Aperture</a> service. This lets you log in to social readers like <a href=\"https://monocle.p3k.io\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Monocle</a> and <a href=\"https://indigenous.abode.pub/ios/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Indigenous</a>.</p>\n<p>This plugin requires the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/indieauth/\" rel=\"ugc\">WordPress IndieAuth plugin</a>. Please ensure that plugin is installed and activated first before attempting to install the Aperture plugin.</p>\n<p>When this plugin is activated, it registers a new account at <a href=\"https://aperture.p3k.io\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Aperture</a>. The <code>&lt;link rel=\"microsub\"&gt;</code> tag is then added to your WordPress site automatically.</p>\n",
